
Cascoon	 A bug type Pokémon

CASCOON makes its protective cocoon 
by wrapping its body entirely with a 
fine silk from its mouth.  Once the silk 
goes around its body, it hardens.  This 
POKéMON prepares for its evolution inside 
the cocoon. 

